description:
Fixed incorrect 1-2-3-4 rhythm that should be 1-2-4-3 at start of second verse.

Fixed interlude where an extra sixteenth note was being used to denote the end of a repetition. The recording is one eighth note (16th - 16th - 8th) instead of two sixteenths (16th - 16th - 16th - 16th) or a rest.

Some notes that should be open were muted.
title: Phantoms
